author: Xbox
description:
Now available in Game Preview! Play now with Game Pass.

The Belfry stands as a beacon of hope and safety amongst the ruins of humanity, where monsters lurk outside the tower’s walls. You are an Ace, born anew from the spirit realm with special skills, grit, and determination. Unite with other Aces*  in a thrilling venture into a new world to protect the people of the Belfry.

Can you become the Ace humanity needs to survive? Join us in Towerborne, a fast-paced, hope-filled, action RPG. In this vibrant world with exhilarating combat, you’ll take on malevolent forces solo or alongside your companions*  and fight as one.

Adventure Together – Venture out of The Belfry solo or with up to three other Aces* to vanquish the looming terror that surrounds the tower. Either way, you won’t be alone. Aces can recruit Umbra companions to join them in battle, gaining access to enhanced skills and unique abilities tied to each spirit. After fighting your way through enemies, return to The Belfry to

author: Xbox
description:
WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers arrives on Xbox Series X|S and Windows July 24, and you can pre-order it today or play it Day One with Game Pass.

Step into a brutal soulslike journey set in the dark final days of the Ming Dynasty. Wuchang, a pirate cursed by the mysterious Feathering, must master ancient spells, powerful weapons, and lost secrets to survive the corrupted world around her.

This new trailer introduces the deadly Bride boss fight, unseen weapon and spell gameplay, and a haunting glimpse of the land of Shu as it collapses into darkness.
